1. Nadam se da ćemo *rešiti* ovaj problem. (I hope we will *solve* this problem.)
2. Pre nego što *rešimo* šta ćemo raditi, treba nam plan. (Before we *decide* what to do, we need a plan.)
3. Molim te, *reši* ovu jednačinu. (Please, *solve* this equation.)
4. Da bismo *rešili* ovaj zadatak, treba nam malo više vremena. (To *solve* this task, we need a little more time.)
5. Konačno smo *rešili* misteriju nestanka ključeva. (We finally *solved* the mystery of the missing keys.)
6. Moramo *rešiti* ovaj problem što pre. (We need to *solve* this problem as soon as possible.)
7. Oni su *rešili* da odu na more za vikend. (They *decided* to go to the seaside for the weekend.)
8. Da li možeš *da rešiš* ovaj test bez pomoći? (Can you *solve* this test without any help?)
9. Koliko vremena ti je potrebno da *rešiš* ovaj zadatak? (How much time do you need to *solve* this task?)
10. Molim vas da *rešite* ovaj problem na miran način. (Please, *solve* this problem peacefully.)